            <span>我要写书评</span>
        </a>
        <h2>
            中国通史选读的书评 · · · · · ·
            <span class="pl">(<a href="reviews">全部 1 条</a>)</span>
        </h2>
    </header>


        


<div class="review-list">
  
  
      
  



  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="3718353">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/3718353/" class="title-link">读《（中国通史选读）纲要》的一点体会</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-3718353"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
